message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. Given its high-quality features and benefits, it's valued at $120. Considering its worth and the value it will bring to you, I kindly propose a special introductory price of $105 for you. This is an excellent opportunity to experience the best of our offerings at a discounted rate. Please let me know if this works for you, and we can proceed with the transaction.
